{"tid":1912136,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"［港台］香港故事 - 追尋人生 星期六 2105-2130","createTime":"2020-03-05T23:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T02:03:05.000Z","uid":30,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92fde281970a8eaa59434696522dd5125fc716c2","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:50:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkstories46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhkstories46&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=17fbae45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkstories46</a><br />\n<br />\n人生由不斷的追尋編織而成。<br />\n有人在事業以外發展另一段平行人生，他們的目標不在於金錢或成就，但同樣的認真、執著，緊扣著社會的脈搏。追尋是一份由心底翻騰而出的動力，牽引著我們尋找人生意義。從九個追尋的故事，啓發我們人生的可能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n07/03/2020<br />\n<br />\n且聽風吟<br />\n<br />\n作曲家鄭靖楠(阿楠)酷愛世界各地的民族音樂，從小收集不同的民族樂器。他自小學時期開始學習西方古典音樂，曾學習小提琴、鋼琴和單簧管，更在大學時期立志成為鋼琴家。豈料一場意外，令他重新審視自己的音樂路向，最後決定改以作曲為志業，並從世界各地的民族音樂中吸收養分。<br />\n<br />\n阿楠甚至上網自學蒙古喉唱「呼麥」，希望將這種肖似草原風聲的元素加入他的現代音樂作品之中。經過數年苦練，阿楠終於能操控泛音，並唱出旋律。他的喉唱風格有別於傳統「呼麥」，使人歎為觀止。<br />\n<br />\n阿楠現時在美國修讀作曲博士，並繼續向世界出發，追尋自己的音樂之路。"},{"pid":"7522a468f0bb9b02386bb73b0eca3d408168e372","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T03:21:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"b09d9cca1d732eb63f4b3aafb3d00329cca63849","tid":1912136,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:26:13.000Z","msg":"(代po) 【突發】推介港台/Viutv節目嘅Instagram上線啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1912701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1912701</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"17a0792fa85c6ca13fd0f21c6a536c463dfba192","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"14/03/2020<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkstories46/episode/625398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fhkstories46%2Fepisode%2F625398&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=a3e8cfc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/hkstories46/episode/625398</a><br />\n<br />\n我執 我不執<br />\n<br />\n熊百祥在大專時對哲學產生興趣，修讀人類學和宗教研究碩士課程讓他更貼近宗教，致令他因想了解不同民族和宗教而學習外語，更遠赴雅典大學修讀希臘文，以及到印度學梵文等。他學習外語，希望化解不同民族和宗教之間的誤會，與人為善。"},{"pid":"425c225350bd720682edc80679248f562e241e46","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T13:24:49.000Z","msg":"條友都幾得閒<br />\n<br />\n學幾種外文"},{"pid":"793bc8b00b485c412861c58009f9dfc83e56820f","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QAiMlCM8Yc4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQAiMlCM8Yc4&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=7f7110c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QAiMlCM8Yc4</a>"},{"pid":"f7a858bf679f425236663067af614ff531d52ded","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"守護天秤<br />\n出身草根階層的大律師黃瑞紅，自幼見盡人情冷暖，深知雪中送炭對弱勢社群的重要。執業以來，她經常為有需要人士提供義務法律支援。她認為法律面前，不論貧富，皆應人人平等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/hkstories46/originals/mfile_8746_625462_6_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fhkstories46%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8746_625462_6_l.jpg&h=03f38bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年十一月，香港理工大學被警方圍堵期間，黃瑞紅幾乎每晚都進入校園，為示威人士提供免費法律諮詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rthk.hk/oldassets/images/rthk/dtt31/hkstories46/originals/mfile_8746_625462_1_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Foldassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Fdtt31%2Fhkstories46%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_8746_625462_1_l.jpg&h=e12f9087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相對入行初期，現有較多的年輕法律工作者願意加入義務法律支援行列，黃瑞紅坦言心感安慰。"},{"pid":"cabf8cad6a609f8f6583e89ef01fff366b44f726","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T12:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17e9436e23279b4d47ba9566f29281e57aca55c","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"出身草根階層嘅大律師 #黃瑞紅，自細見盡人情冷暖，深知雪中送炭對弱勢社群嘅重要。執業以來，佢成日為有需要人士提供義務法律支援。佢認為法律面前，不論貧富，都應該人人平等。<br />\n<br />\n因為近年社會事件，黃瑞紅係警署常客，佢義助被告人士，向佢哋解釋公民權利、聽取申訴，同時亦係心靈上嘅安撫。佢某次曾經喺庭上求情時引述魯迅：「勇者憤怒，抽刃向更強者；怯者憤怒，卻抽刃向更弱者」......<br />\n<br />\n今晚（星期六）9pm #港台電視31 今輯最後一集嘅《香港故事─追尋人生》，有黃瑞紅守護天秤嘅故事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/549206479049760/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHK.HK%2Fvideos%2F549206479049760%2F&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=f6d329a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.HK/videos/549206479049760/</a>"},{"pid":"daeb0061447eecc2298c741fcf07f10cb263180d","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"531f31a5d3d315b433c14fcd5da6591ef05ecf3f","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3999fc761ec84ad466ac80d0ebcc46cad9bcdde9","tid":1912136,"uid":30,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T13:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a69